## Use policy
- Do not require paid IDEs for end users.
- Do not bundle IDE installers into the app package.
- Keep Python/Streamlit/Pillow/pandas/Jinja2 as the actual runtime stack.
- Use Visual Studio, WebStorm, Android Studio, Xcode, CLion, Rider, IntelliJ, Eclipse, and NetBeans only by role.
- Store no raw API keys.
